HEADWORD: Jimp
<hw>Jimp</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Gimp</er>,
<pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Neat; handsome; elegant. See
<er>Gimp</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
